<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:14:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>百胜中国首席财务官辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</link><description>百胜中国控股表示，财务总监杨安迪因个人原因打算辞职，该辞职将于9月30日生效。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 称法院应拒绝司法部在剥离诉讼中提交的秘密文件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</link><description>TikTok 及其母公司字节跳动周一要求美国上诉法院驳回司法部秘密提起部分法律诉讼的请求，该诉讼捍卫了一项寻求在 1 月 19 日之前强制剥离 TikTok 美国资产或实施禁令的法律。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球股市暴跌的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，全球股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，同时押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大获得针对高管的禁令，旨在追回60亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大周一表示，这家负债累累的房地产开发商已获得针对三名高管的禁令，并寻求从针对七名人士的法律诉讼中追回约 60 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手邹敬源卫冕双杠冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，中国选手邹敬源轻松击败对手，卫冕奥运会双杠冠军，获得巴黎奥运会上的第三枚奖牌，为中国队赢得了体操项目的第二枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 10:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球单打决赛韩国选手安赛龙、丹麦选手安赛龙夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-skoreas-an-beats-chinas-he-claim-womens-singles-gold-2024-08-05/</link><description>韩国选手安世英以21-13 21-16击败中国选手何冰娇，夺得羽毛球女单奥运金牌；丹麦选手安赛龙则以11-21 11-21击败泰国选手昆拉武特·维蒂萨恩，成功卫冕男子羽毛球项目冠军。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 09:58:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-skoreas-an-beats-chinas-he-claim-womens-singles-gold-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>冰球中国击败澳大利亚，荷兰，阿根廷和比利时也进入半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/hockey-china-upset-australia-advance-semis-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，中国女子曲棍球队在巴黎奥运会上以3比2击败澳大利亚队，在失球的情况下迅速恢复，时隔16年首次进入半决赛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 09:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/hockey-china-upset-australia-advance-semis-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手李娜夺得25米手枪速射金牌 意大利队夺得双向飞碟混合团体赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-li-wins-gold-mens-25m-rapid-fire-pistol-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，意大利组合加布里埃莱·罗塞蒂和戴安娜·巴科西在巴黎奥运会射击双向飞碟项目决赛中夺冠，美国名将文森特·汉考克距离第五枚奥运会金牌还差之毫厘。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-li-wins-gold-mens-25m-rapid-fire-pistol-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>监测组织称，中国无人驾驶军机在越南海岸附近被追踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uncrewed-chinese-military-aircraft-tracked-close-vietnam-coast-monitor-group-2024-08-05/</link><description>南海研究机构告诉路透社，上周，一架打开跟踪器的中国军用无人驾驶飞机在越南海岸附近飞行，这是该组织五年来的监测中，北京首次公开此类行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uncrewed-chinese-military-aircraft-tracked-close-vietnam-coast-monitor-group-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求大型国有金融机构放弃审计师普华永道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-large-state-financial-institutions-drop-auditor-pwc-say-sources-2024-08-05/</link><description>两位消息人士称，近几个月来，中国监管机构已要求普华永道 (PwC) 的几家大型国有客户放弃该审计师，因为该审计师准备因其为陷入困境的房地产开发商恒大集团所做的工作而受到处罚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-large-state-financial-institutions-drop-auditor-pwc-say-sources-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>美军着眼澳大利亚印度洋脚趾以威慑中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-eyes-australias-indian-ocean-toe-hold-deter-china-2024-08-05/</link><description>澳大利亚一个偏远岛屿靠近中国石油运输的印度洋咽喉要道，该岛被列入美国可能进行军事建设的地点清单，旨在威慑中国，美国表示该岛“可能会也可能不会”支持美国军队。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-eyes-australias-indian-ocean-toe-hold-deter-china-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，中国结婚夫妇数量降至12年来最低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/number-chinese-couples-getting-married-falls-12-year-low-data-shows-2024-08-05/</link><description>官方数据显示，由于经济放缓和生活成本上升，越来越多的年轻人推迟结婚，今年上半年中国结婚人数降至2013年以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/number-chinese-couples-getting-married-falls-12-year-low-data-shows-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国荣耀在准备首次公开募股时获得了“异常”强大的国家支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-honor-gets-strong-state-backing-it-readies-ipo-2024-08-05/</link><description>据政策文件和知情人士透露，随着前华为 (HWT.UL) 子公司准备首次公开募股 (IPO)，中国智能手机制造商荣耀正获得当地政府支持者“不同寻常”的高水平支持。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:15:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-honor-gets-strong-state-backing-it-readies-ipo-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球股市暴跌的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，全球股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，同时押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国东部创纪录气温，电力需求激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国东部地区遭遇反常高温，预计江苏和浙江等高度工业化省份的沿海大城市将持续长达10天的高温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>